text: Athaba tomaloke e'i bisaye niscinta haicha neki ye, te'om tomalokaka dbitiyabara sagarata lai nayaba arau tomalokara biraud'dhe pracanda dhumuha napathaba arau tomalokara kupharai karaara babe tomalokaka te'om duba'i namaraiba? Tara pichata tomaloke amara biraud'dhe kono sahayakarai bicarai napaba
